ed>μφαλιούνε<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied>ος ⟦---⟧ <lb n="15"/><supplied reason="lost">ἐν τὰν ἐπισκευὰν καὶ κατα</supplied>σκευὰν τοῦν τειχέουν πλινθευ<lb break="no" n="16"/><supplied reason="lost">σέμεν δουριὰν ἐν τοῦ</supplied> ἐνεστάκοντι ἐνιαυτοῦ ἐς τοῖ ἰδίοι <lb n="17"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ⟦---⟧ μυριάδα παρεχόνσας τᾶς π<supplied reason="lost">ό</supplied><lb break="no" n="18"/><supplied reason="lost">λιος <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied>ος ἐς τοῦν δεύσει πλινθευέμεν ΚΑ<lb break="no" n="19"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>Α ἐπανγέλλανθο μὰ οὑσαύτους ΚΑ<lb break="no" n="20"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>αιος πλινθευσέμεν δουριὰν ἐπὶ Ε<lb break="no" n="21"/><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> σ</supplied>τραταγὸν Πόλλιχον τὸν ἐνια<supplied reason="lost">υ</supplied><lb break="no" n="22"/><supplied reason="lost">τὸν <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied>δας δύας καὶ Ἱππόλοχος Ἀλε<lb break="no" n="23"/><supplied reason="lost">ξίππειος καὶ Κρατῖνο</supplied>ς Κλεομαχίδαιος καὶ Με<lb break="no" n="24"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="25"/>⟦---⟧ <lb n="26"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Κόττυφος <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="27"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>Α ΣΤΡΑΤ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="28"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>Α οὕστ<supplied reason="lost">ε <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="29"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ΓΕΛ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
